<h1>There have been changes to Account# <%= @account.id %>, at BankAndTrust.com, <%= @user.first_name %></h1>

<p>There has been a recent change in your account!</p>

<div>
	<h3>Update is as follows:</h3>
	<p>===============================</p>
	<p>Transaction Date: <%= @account.updated_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
	<p>Account Number: <%= @account.id %></p>
	<p>Account Type: <%= @account.account_type %></p>
	<p>Transaction Type: <%= @transaction %></p>
	<p>Amount of Transaction: <%= number_to_currency @amount %></p>
	<p>Previous Balance: <%= number_to_currency @previous_balance %></p>
	<p>Current Balance: <%= number_to_currency @account.balance %></p>
</div>
  
<div>
	<p>If this change has occured in error please reach out to us immediately at <%= @url %>.</p>

	<p>Otherwise, we appreciate your business and hope you continue to enjoy banking with us.</p>
</div>